text: Anika Schwörer (born 1 June 2001) is a Swiss volleyball player. She is a member of the Women's National Team. She participated at the 2018 Montreux Volley Masters. She plays for Sm’Aesch Pfeffingen. == Clubs == * Volley Smash 05 (2018) * Sm’Aesch Pfeffingen (2019) == References == == External links == * FIVB Profile * * Anika Schwörer neu in der Damen-Nationalmannschaft * Anika Schwörer: «Ich bin sehr ehrgeizig, was meine Stärke und meine Schwäche ist» Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
